{"tid":2411541,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做過兩間花店 你問我答","createTime":"2021-02-17T11:40:52.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-16T10:58:55.000Z","uid":296936,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"4d5b2bacdc8927edcad8f607ce7f9f6ce012ba1d","tid":2411541,"uid":296936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:40:52.000Z","msg":"想答會答 可能唔答"},{"pid":"d47d64b09cb83f6fa0f55cce2701d1e920787f8c","tid":2411541,"uid":294782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"2月生意額=其他月份幾多個月？"},{"pid":"66c33626d3f9f7aa754dc45cdbc8831d4c6996e7","tid":2411541,"uid":181651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:44:19.000Z","msg":"點入行？"},{"pid":"5866aaa774bbad5e68b5951fbf3c414084c3766f","tid":2411541,"uid":296936,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d47d64b09cb83f6fa0f55cce2701d1e920787f8c","tid":2411541,"uid":294782,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:43:30.000Z","msg":"2月生意額=其他月份幾多個月？"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:45:08.000Z","msg":"平時$50 蚊十枝大陸玫瑰<br />\n情人節$150 十枝"},{"pid":"a25f2be96491eb93079f0a731fb7dfaa7fb09672","tid":2411541,"uid":296936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"66c33626d3f9f7aa754dc45cdbc8831d4c6996e7","tid":2411541,"uid":181651,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:44:19.000Z","msg":"點入行？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:45:28.000Z","msg":"去花店見工"},{"pid":"12b5b974ee822c10259b2240330cdf404ef39ad0","tid":2411541,"uid":86378,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-17T11:46:02.000Z","msg":"點分邊啲花雪過？<br />\n買過啲雪花，超快殘"},{"pid":"5325b578f5407bf42430ad56cc66afc9832a1606","tid":2411541,"uid":294782,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5866aaa774bbad5e68b5951fbf3c414084c3766f","tid":2411541,"uid":296936,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"quote":{"pid":"d47d64b09cb83f6fa0f55cce2701d1e920787f8c","tid":2411541,"uid":294782,"like":1,"disli